# コミットメッセージ自動生成（ソース管理の ✨ ボタン）

Generate commit messages in Japanese.

- Use Conventional Commits prefixes: feat:, fix:, refactor:, docs:, chore:
- Write the description in Japanese (not English)
- Keep the first line concise; focus on why the change was made

Examples:
- feat: Turnstileのサイトキー検証を追加
- fix: 本番ContactのTurnstile表示を修正
